{"tid":2487051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網路平台販售「別開槍 我不是中國人」T恤 中媒氣罵：歧視中國人","createTime":"2021-04-13T09:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T10:45:25.000Z","uid":32511,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1290211b2823f992b073bc0d5f5f8bad6e823f8f","tid":2487051,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQGwHzFLjgmFJE4E6jEM9zzihEYRk6FL1Xt5iG6k8RhMo?filename=6CuxA87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CuxA87.png&h=e8e15fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYBXQaHNtutU67XdfyL8PJwTgyDSULbNm1FBEE5rDAC4y?filename=CL0Ef89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCL0Ef89.png&h=52689bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmchpbGvidJRZLqaTnFURFCpfSE4p7gaKY9R2UK9BH7acz?filename=Xh4JHPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXh4JHPa.png&h=a8378a49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVSF5RutjQ9n6uHP8wPSmTHLFsVjX1qE1NCugcm7CtLJF?filename=4UR79uc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR79uc.png&h=2f5be137&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWDFFhcrHfNgXxAHfeQtzgLaNH7juqWp8SCCx4E1iDgqT?filename=kVQ5bHy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVQ5bHy.png&h=bf0dee7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVdeAX5L3uNxVvHUYQLNSsxk1AfXRSTjVsaaWM2gYkc74?filename=U5KUPue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5KUPue.png&h=42ee8b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2006年創立於澳洲墨爾本的創意設計商品平台Redbubble，專門為獨立藝術家提供一處可讓<br />\n他們發揮的天地，有超過70萬個獨立藝術家在Redbubble上分享精采作品，從衣服、壁貼、<br />\n口罩、手機殼......各式各樣的創意小物都有。但近日該平台上出現了讓中國官媒《環球時<br />\n報》大動肝火的產品，此外，一些網路平台另有一系列印有「I'M NOT CHINESE」（我不是<br />\n中國人）的T恤跟相關商品，讓中共官方喉舌《環球時報》氣得大罵是在歧視中國人。<br />\n <br />\n在Redbubble上搜尋關鍵字就可以找到許多印有強調自己「不是中國人」字樣的衣服，有的<br />\n聲明自己是韓國人、緬甸人、馬來西亞人、新加坡人，總之不是中國人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/newtalk.tw/news/view/amp/2021-04-13/562780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Famp%2F2021-04-13%2F562780&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11P5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=8e18c221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/newtalk.tw/news/view/amp/2021-04-13/562780</a>"},{"pid":"981ddcd818346fd2918e9d40a16cb18b31f88681","tid":2487051,"uid":379905,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"有discount嘅話小粉紅會唔會爭住買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d647f3406ab1e970ab784b1d19f900f14fe8162","tid":2487051,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最中意睇頭條、hk01<br />\n<br />\n食元氣東海堂<br />\n<br />\n買小米華為<br />\n<br />\n用富途牛牛<br />\n<br />\n總之我係中國人呀HI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0ab49e34a3ff5d690a1bf619e8d5b7bf25b66b","tid":2487051,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981ddcd818346fd2918e9d40a16cb18b31f88681","tid":2487051,"uid":379905,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"有discount嘅話小粉紅會唔會爭住買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7514c97cfef6d52c91386546207dd1f6504cd7f","tid":2487051,"uid":88133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"有無香港"},{"pid":"4b098ff7479b9653af0e93c7b54407a2088e0a21","tid":2487051,"uid":370061,"like